a tremendous sacrifice for his country.

21:50.559 --> 21:52.060
And for the rest of us.

21:52.228 --> 21:55.846
Hey, hey, hey. Hey, it's okay.

21:58.234 --> 22:00.941
It's more than okay. It's great.

22:02.655 --> 22:05.112
