22:05.533 --> 22:07.569
-Coby and Lisa are good.
-Yeah.

22:07.743 --> 22:11.611
-My armadillo Felix is good.
-Yeah.

22:11.789 --> 22:14.781
-And now we're okay.
-Yup. Yup, we are.

22:14.959 --> 22:18.247
