get any better.

22:18.796 --> 22:24.086
I swear, sometimes I feel so lucky.

22:25.052 --> 22:26.167
-Right.
-And so grateful.

22:26.595 --> 22:29.678
And I feel it so hard,
I think it's just gonna split me in half.

22:30.599 --> 22:33.056
-Right.
-And I don't ever want it to stop.

22:33.853 --> 22:35.059
You know?

22:35.396 --> 22:37.261
Not really, but I'm happy for you.

22:45.823 --> 22:47.154
Hey, Tommy.

22:47.324 --> 22:50.157
How come you're not answering
the phone?

22:55.958 --> 22:58.449
[FAUCET RUNNING]

23:27.197 --> 23:29.734
[DOGS BARKING IN DISTANCE]

23:33.495 --> 23:35.486
