23:36.957 --> 23:38.538
Or I can follow in my own car.

23:39.627 --> 23:42.539
Sheriff, you're injured.
You'd be a liability.

23:42.713 --> 23:44.544
Of course, Sir.

23:44.715 --> 23:47.172
Need me to do anything on this end?

23:47.343 --> 23:51.006
Run to the store,
grab me a pack of Luckies.

23:57.269 --> 23:58.770
AN DY:
Asshole.

23:58.938 --> 24:00.599
FELTON:
I ought to kill you motherfuckers.

24:00.773 --> 24:04.561
I felt kind of bad shooting my own daddy.
I ain't gonna feel nothing shooting you.

24:04.735 --> 24:07.021
Put the gun down.
Nobody needs to get hurt.

24:07.196 --> 24:08.527
Maybe I like hurting people.

24:09.365 --> 24:13.358
That's the blood talking.
Look at me. I've been there, man.

24:13.535 --> 24:15.742
It's lying to you.
You don't wanna hurt anybody.

24:15.913 --> 24:18.450
-You don't know what I want!
-I know you want more V.

24:19.124 --> 24:22.082
Ain't nobody here gonna try to stop you
from taking it with you.

24:22.252 --> 24:25.335
Say goodbye to my woman,
because she's coming with me.

24:25.506 --> 24:28.748
