42:06.774 --> 42:08.389
You wanna live together?

42:09.193 --> 42:10.569
I wanna marry you.

42:12.405 --> 42:14.270
But, uh, we can't.

42:14.824 --> 42:15.984
Says who?

42:16.617 --> 42:18.653
People become ministers on the Internet.

42:19.620 --> 42:22.987
So, what's to keep me from becoming
a minister and marrying us myself?

42:27.253 --> 42:29.118
I love you so much.

42:35.636 --> 42:37.376
I don't know what I'd do without you.

42:38.306 --> 42:40.797
Well, it's lucky for you
you'll never have to find out.

42:45.521 --> 42:47.227
[JESSICA SQUEALS]

42:48.066 --> 42:50.102
[BOTH LAUGHING]

42:50.276 --> 42:51.686
JESSICA:
No!

42:52.612 --> 42:55.445
[CHATTERING]

43:11.714 --> 43:13.045
[KNOCKING]

43:18.262 --> 43:19.297
We must talk.

43:20.348 --> 43:21.383
Come in.

43:39.325 --> 43:40.531
Russell is gone.

43:41.035 --> 43:42.616
Thank God for small favors.

43:42.787 --> 43:43.867
Eric as well.

43:44.747 --> 43:46.703
-What?
-I ended him.

43:48.042 --> 43:49.077
Why?

43:50.211 --> 43:52.167
He tasted you.

43:52.880 --> 43:54.165
He knew what you are.

43:55.383 --> 43:59.342
Even if we are to go our separate ways,
I will make sure that you are safe.

43:59.512 --> 44:04.006
-But Eric would never--
-Sookie, most vampires are not like me.

44:04.433 --> 44:08.847
Even if holding themselves back occurred to
them, they would probably not be able to.

44:11.691 --> 44:14.353
I'm not taking any chances.

44:14.902 --> 44:19.737
I intend to bring the true death to all that
have tasted you and know what you are.

44:19.907 --> 44:22.740
Russell, Eric....

44:22.910 --> 44:27.244
Pam, the queen,
and any who discover it in the future.

44:28.249 --> 44:31.082
I will do anything to keep you safe...

44:31.460 --> 44:33.917
...even if it means
me not being a part of your life.

44:36.549 --> 44:38.210
This I swear to you.

44:46.100 --> 44:51.766
I have never loved, nor will I ever love,
as I have loved you.

44:56.444 --> 44:59.356
Wait. Don't go.

45:00.573 --> 45:05.943
Did you tell her you were originally sent
by the Queen of Louisiana to procure her...

45:06.120 --> 45:07.656
...because of what She might be?

45:09.373 --> 45:10.704
What?

45:11.125 --> 45:13.161
I did not know why she wanted you.

45:14.420 --> 45:18.333
As I grew to know you,
I purposely kept you from her.

45:18.507 --> 45:20.088
Were you ever gonna tell me?

45:21.219 --> 45:24.427
I hoped to someday. I swear it.

45:24.597 --> 45:28.181
What about you letting two psychos
beat her within an inch of her life...

45:28.351 --> 45:31.388
...so you could feed her your blood
the night you met?

45:31.562 --> 45:33.518
Think she'll forgive you for that?

45:34.148 --> 45:37.015
[GRUNTING]

45:41.989 --> 45:43.320
Oh, my God.

45:43.491 --> 45:45.823
-Sookie--
-Is it true?

45:49.247 --> 45:50.282
Yes.

45:52.166 --> 45:54.873
He tried to silence me tonight
so you would never know.

45:55.586 --> 45:57.451
He doesn't wanna protect you.

45:57.630 --> 45:59.291
He only wants to protect himself.

46:00.466 --> 46:02.548
-Get out of my house.
-Please.

46:02.718 --> 46:04.003
Don't ever come here.

46:04.178 --> 46:05.384
Don't ever call me.

46:05.554 --> 46:08.762
Don't ever talk to me. Ever.

46:08.975 --> 46:12.058
You manipulated me
into falling in love with you.

46:12.228 --> 46:15.766
It is who you are, Sookie,
not what you are, that I love...

46:16.691 --> 46:20.024
...and will love always,
until I meet the true death.

46:20.194 --> 46:24.483
Love?! You don't even get
to use that word.

46:25.032 --> 46:27.489
-| rescind my invitation.
-No!

46:35.209 --> 46:36.824
I want my phone back.

46:45.219 --> 46:49.383
You too. Get the fuck off my porch
and out of my life.

46:49.807 --> 46:52.674
For the record, I would never have
given you to Russell.

46:52.852 --> 46:57.346
Go back to hell where you came from,
you fucking dead piece of Shit.

47:01.235 --> 47:05.899
I'm sorry to see you suffer like this,
but I thought you had the right to know.

47:44.487 --> 47:45.897
Did you kill him?

47:46.072 --> 47:50.111
Please tell me you killed him, because I will
never get all the cement out of my hair.

47:50.284 --> 47:52.195
I gave him a much worse punishment.

47:52.370 --> 47:54.827
Ruben tried to kill me, by the way.

47:55.122 --> 47:56.282
I took him out.

47:58.042 --> 47:59.202
[SIGHS]

47:59.377 --> 48:02.619
Oh, great. On top of everything,
I'm out an assassin.

48:02.797 --> 48:04.503
I have zero patience with that shit.

48:26.570 --> 48:28.356
SAM:
Tommy, come back here!

48:37.456 --> 48:38.741
Fuck!

48:42.002 --> 48:43.617
So now you're gonna shoot me?

48:47.258 --> 48:48.464
Give my money back.

48:49.593 --> 48:51.174
Fuck you.

48:51.345 --> 48:54.633
You came along, changed my whole life.

48:55.516 --> 48:57.177
Took away everything I knew.

48:58.102 --> 49:00.684
And now you're just throwing me away
like garbage.

49:00.855 --> 49:03.688
I think I might have saved your life,
you stupid little shit.

49:03.858 --> 49:07.942
Yeah, stupid. Good, rub it in!

49:08.904 --> 49:10.155
Just give me my money.

49:10.322 --> 49:13.189
-How am I supposed to live?
-Get a job.

49:15.035 --> 49:16.536
I can't fucking read.

49:16.704 --> 49:18.194
Not my problem.

49:22.376 --> 49:23.491
Fuck you.

49:26.547 --> 49:29.539
You ain't gonna shoot shit.

50:10.299 --> 50:13.416
-Your Majesty.
-Hm.

50:14.345 --> 50:17.257
We'll sidestep your recent defection.

50:18.265 --> 50:19.971
For now.

50:21.435 --> 50:25.144
Tell me, do I make a good widow?

50:25.314 --> 50:26.599
You are a vision.

50:27.441 --> 50:32.777
Bill, don't be such a sourpuss.

50:33.781 --> 50:36.193
Aren't you the least bit excited?

50:36.367 --> 50:38.949
Russell is no more.

50:39.119 --> 50:41.246
I am pleased, yes.

50:41.914 --> 50:46.624
Dear me. How dreary you are.

50:48.087 --> 50:51.079
All right, bring me the girl.

50:52.383 --> 50:55.466
I have waited centuries to find a true fae.

50:56.845 --> 51:00.337
I can't wait to feel
the sunlight on my skin again.

51:01.308 --> 51:03.094
Maybe I'll get a yacht.

51:03.811 --> 51:05.597
Sookie is not here.

51:07.106 --> 51:12.146
Yes, I brought you here
under false pretenses.

51:12.778 --> 51:14.769
But I do have another surprise for you.

51:16.490 --> 51:18.481
Only one of us will leave this house.

51:21.495 --> 51:25.659
You dare challenge me?

51:26.875 --> 51:29.207
I'm over twice your age.

51:29.670 --> 51:31.285
Yes.

51:32.590 --> 51:34.922
But I have nothing left to lose.

51:35.092 --> 51:37.674
[GROWLING]

51:57.698 --> 52:02.192
Gran, I am so lost.

52:04.246 --> 52:09.616
I followed my heart,
but it led me down a dead-end road.

52:13.213 --> 52:15.955
I miss you so much.

52:18.218 --> 52:21.051
I've never felt so alone.

52:24.600 --> 52:28.138
And I've spent my whole life
feeling alone.

52:30.230 --> 52:32.061
WOMAN:
SooMe.

52:32.232 --> 52:34.063
You're not alone.

52:35.611 --> 52:36.896
Come with us.
